 nutation phenomenon\nif the secondary black hole has a mass higher than about six times that of the\nprimary black hole.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Oct 2012 14:07:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
